    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily transportation. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are solid and have been maintained to ensure dependable performance. However, potential buyers should expect some visible wear and tear consistent with its age, including minor scratches on the exterior and some fading in the interior upholstery. It\u2019s a functional car that gets the job done without the price tag of a newer model.",
